name: SupDuck 1619
description:
**BEHOLD! THE WACKENING!**

This SupDuck has become Super Wacky from licking a MegaToad in [Dr. Drool's Lab](https://supducks.com/wackyducks). Having officially blasted off to a parallel universe, this Duck will now be seen in the eyes of the DuckGod as a Duck who has become Enlightened. With Enlightenment comes great responsibility and privileged perks.

**Wacky Level:** 3

**Image Links:**

[OG Duck Image](ipfs://QmPeTSwPryCfHgUePSSSYinJPiYiwMuRwPyUGJZjLy7txQ)

[Static Wacky Image](https://api.supducks.com/supducks/png/3/1619)

asset_contract.name: SupDucks
asset_contract.description:
Cool duck says Sup! Launched July 17th, 2021 by **MegaVolt Corp.** SupDucks are a 10,000 randomly generated collection that grants you access to the SupDucks Ecosystem. 

Every duck in the pond needs a friend so the DuckGod created KingFrogs and MegaToads, your Ducks BFFs! Each SupDuck doubles as a community pass to Discord, LiveStreams, IRL Events, $VOLT and gives each holder the opportunity to be a part of building the SupDucks MetaVerse.

Stay up to date: 
**
[Twitter](https://twitter.com/realsupducks) |

[Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa-nNLetADH7iGdvqzIIqSg)**
